-- Arcelormittal Said to Hire Banks for Bond Investor Call Today
-- B y   K a t i e   L i n s e l l
-- 2012-03-21T12:56:06Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-21/arcelormittal-said-to-hire-banks-for-bond-investor-call-today.html
ArcelorMittal (MT)  SA hired Credit
Agricole CIB, Commerzbank AG,  HSBC Holdings Plc (HSBA)  and Societe
Generale CIB to arrange an investor conference call for 2:30
p.m. in London, according to a banker involved in the meeting. A
euro-denominated issue may follow the call.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Katie Linsell in London at 
 klinsell@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andrew Reierson at 
 areierson1@bloomberg.net  